  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AlreadyBuiltException
    exception thrown if the worker has already build
    AlreadyChosenStarterException
    exception thrown if a starting player has already been chosen
    AlreadyPresentPlayerException
    exception thrown if a player with the same characteristics already exists in the match
    AlreadyWalkedException
    exception thrown if the workr has already walked
    endedMoveException
    exception thrown if the move has ended
    IllegalBlockUpdateException
    exception thrown if the a player try to update the block in an illegal way
    IllegalBuildingException
    exception thrown if the building is not allowed
    IllegalMovementException
    exception thrown if the movement is not allowed
    InvalidCardException
    exception thrown if the selected card is not valid
    InvalidNamePlayerException
    exception thrown if the player's nickname is not valid
    InvalidTypeOfMatch
    exception thrown if the set type of match (2 or 3 players) is not valid
    NoMoreCardsException
    exception thrown if no more cards can be added to the chosen cards
    NoMorePlayersException
    exception thrown if no more players can be added to the game
    NoPlayerException
    exception thrown if there are no players in the match
    NoStarterException
    exception thrown if there isn't a selected starting player
    NotPossibleEndMoveException
    exception thrown if the end move is not allowed
    OpponentEffectException
    exception thrown if a movement is allowed because of an Opponent Effect
    OutOfOrderMoveException
    exception thrown if the selected move can not be done in that moment
